•• To stop specific Network Devices: 
ifdown eth0•••

•• To start a specific Device: 
ifuo eth0

••Shutdown all Network Interfaces:
# /etc/init.d/network stop

••To start all Network Interfaces:
# /etc/init.d/network start

••For Security to secure your Services make this file immunized.
# chattr +I /etc/services
🚨This will prevent unauthorized access!